::Rex::

Rex raises an eyebrow at Feline's reaction, glancing at the spare parts as 
they dropped to the floor. He looks at her, wondering why she was reacting 
like that. He blinks as he realizes it, looking down at his own mean-looking 
gun.

"Um, sorry," he says, putting it away, "I couldn't be sure that you were not 
an invader. The Predacons have tried to sneak in here recently, we caught 
them though."

He looks at her. "Are you allright?"
